<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Africoin - The Digital Spine of Africa</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --navy: #0a0e1a; --gold: #FFB800; --cyan: #00D4FF; --white: #ffffff; --surface: #16203a; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); line-height: 1.6; }
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 20px 8%; background: rgba(10,14,26,0.95); border-bottom: 1px solid #222; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 20px; margin: 0; }
        .nav-links a { color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: 0.3s; }
        .hero { padding: 100px 8%; text-align: center; background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #16203a 0%, #0a0e1a 100%); }
        .hero-tag { color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--gold); padding: 5px 15px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
        h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); margin: 0 0 20px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; }
        .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .stat-card { background: var(--surface); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; min-width: 140px; }
        .stat-value { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; display: block; }
        .stat-label { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .section { padding: 80px 8%; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; }
        .card { background: var(--surface); padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid #222; }
        .cta-button { padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; transition: 0.3s; }
        .primary { background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); }
        .secondary { border: 2px solid #333; color: white; margin-left: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo"><i class="fas fa-train"></i> Africoin <span style="color:var(--cyan)">Spine</span></a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#spine">Architecture</a></li>
            <li><a href="#sentinel">Sentinel</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tokenomics">Economics</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dashboard.html" style="color:var(--gold)">Dashboard</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-tag">2026 CONTINENTAL ROLLOUT</div>
        <h1>Built for Africa, By Africa</h1>
        <p style="color:#aaa; max-width:700px; margin: 0 auto 40px;">Integrated high-speed rail and Sui blockchain network, securing trade for 54 nations.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-value">10B</span><span class="stat-label">AFRC Supply</span></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-value">54</span><span class="stat-label">Member States</span></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-value">$250K+</span><span class="stat-label">Throughput</span></div>
        </div>
        <a href="#sentinel" class="cta-button primary">Launch Sentinel App</a>
    </section>
    <section id="spine" class="section">
        <h2 style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px;">The Digital Spine Architecture</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card"><h3>Sui Move Ledger</h3><p>Logic-based assets ensure freight manifests and tickets are unique digital objects.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Go Ingest Engine</h3><p>Processes real-time GPS telemetry from every locomotive on the continent.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="sentinel" class="section" style="background: #0d121f;">
        <div class="grid">
            <div>
                <h2 style="color:var(--gold)">Sentinel Mobile Suite</h2>
                <p>Empowering 2,000+ track workers with Proof-of-Safety reporting and instant AFRC rewards.</p>
                <a href="/dashboard.html" class="cta-button primary">Open Sentinel Portal</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <p>AFRC Sentinel Wallet</p>
                <h2 style="color:var(--cyan)">150.00 AFRC</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="tokenomics" class="section">
        <h2 style="text-align:center;">1% Burn Flywheel</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card"><h3>Distribution</h3><p>45% Community & Sentinels, 20% Ecosystem Fund, 8% Core Tech Staff.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Mechanism</h3><p>Every ton of freight moved triggers a 1% burn, increasing token scarcity.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer style="padding: 60px 8%; border-top: 1px solid #222; background: #0a0e1a;">
        <h4 style="color:var(--gold)">Contact: ben.mpolokoso@gmail.com</h4>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#888;">Â© 2025 Africoin Spine Infrastructure Project</p>
    </footer>
</body></html>
